// WSPR beacon with WM-386 (ESP6288 clone), SI5351, SSD1306 0.91" or SH1106 1.3", TinyGSP (optional)
// Original idea from Benno PA3FBX and adapted by PD8GB, PA3FEX and PA3ANG


